Customer Service
================
Trade Action
============
BUY
===
1. Deduct  amount from Customer balance.
2. Add an entry into portfolio_item table (if no records found).
3. Increase the quantity in the portfolio_item table (if a record is found).

SELL
====
1. Credit amount to customer balance.
2. Deduct quantity sold in the portfolio_item table.

Exceptions
==========
1. Customer NOT FOUND
2. Customer does NOT have enough balance
3. Customer does NOT have enough shares
4. Return the error as Problem Detail
   a. 4XX error.